               <p>GEORGE RUTHVEN. I am an officer; on Monday, the 25th of November, I was under the Piazza, Cnvent-garden, I saw the prisoner take the handkerchief from the pocket of a gentleman. I secured him.</p>
               <p>Cross-examined. I am sure I saw him take it.</p>
